Detailed Description

This class does all the tasks involved in going up and down a level in the routing.

That includes finding origina and destination nodes on higher level, and keeping track of which maps to route on after routing on higher level.

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum LevelTransitObject::state_t [private]
 

Enumeration values:
FINDING_MAPS  The state that is entered at the start.

In this state the maps to route to are requested.

FINDING_NODES  When in this state, the edge nodes are requested as well as the overview mapID.
TRANSLATING_NODES  Map the nodes up one level.
DONE  We have finished the finding.
